《月光光心慌慌》於1979年由{{link-en|科幻、奇幻及恐怖電影學院|Academy of Science Fiction, Fantasy & Horror Films}}提名至{{link-en|土星獎恐怖電影得獎列表|Saturn Award for Best Horror Film|最佳恐怖電影}}，但不敵《[[異教徒_(1973年電影)|異教徒]]》（1973年）<ref>Saturn Award Nominees and Winners, 1979 at [http://imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_of_Science_Fiction_Fantasy_And_Horror_Films_USA/1979 Internet Movie Database] {{Wayback|url=http://imdb.com/Sections/Awards/Academy_of_Science_Fiction_Fantasy_And_Horror_Films_USA/1979 |date=20040629013109 }}; last accessed April 19, 2006.</ref>。2001年，電影在[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]評選出的[[AFI百年百大驚悚電影|百年百大驚悚電影]]中名列第68名<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/docs/tvevents/pdf/thrills100.pdf |title=AFI's 100 Years... 100 Thrills |publisher=afi.com |date= |accessdate=2010-05-22 |archive-date=2016-06-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160629221917/http://www.afi.com/Docs/tvevents/pdf/thrills100.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而在[[美國精彩電視台|美國精彩電視台]]選出的{{link-en|最佳百大恐怖電影瞬間|The 100 Scariest Movie Moments}}（2004年）排名第14<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bravotv.com/The_100_Scariest_Movie_Moments/index.shtml  |title= ''Bravo's'' 100 Scariest Movie Moments |publisher=web.archive.org |date= |accessdate=2010-05-22 |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20071030070540/http://www.bravotv.com/The_100_Scariest_Movie_Moments/index.shtml |archivedate = 2007-10-30}}</ref>。2006年，電影因「重要文化、歷史和美學價值」為由，獲[[國會圖書館_(美國)|美國國家圖書館]]列入[[國家電影登記表|國家電影登記表]]之中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.horror-movies.ca/horror_7149.html |title=''Halloween'' Added to the National Film Registry |publisher=Horror Movies, CA |date= |accessdate=2010-05-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100405030121/http://www.horror-movies.ca/horror_7149.html |archivedate=2010-04-05 }}</ref>。2008年，《月光光心慌慌》名列[[帝國雜誌|帝國雜誌]]「有史以來最偉大的500部電影」之一<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.empireonline.com/500/8.asp |title=Empire's 500 Greatest Movies of All Time |publisher=[[Empire_(magazine)|Empire]] |date= |accessdate=2011-07-31 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924011902/http://www.empireonline.com/500/8.asp |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

